IDEAS

- Having Several Diferent Libraries

	NEW CLASSES
		- LibraryManager.java (readernotes.src.core)
		- LibraryIO.java (readernotes.src.database) (Old IOManager.java)
	CHANGED CLASSES
		- IOManager.java (To Deal with Several Libraries)
	NEW FEATURES
		- New Library
		- Delete Library
		- Edit Library

--> The application should only load one library at a time, not allowing to
hava multiple Libraries loaded in memory at the same time. 

